Nobody has made an entire organ yet but you can do a lot with just the cells.
Geron has already manufactured mouse heart muscle cells from mouse stem cells,
when the muscle cells were injected into a living mouse they found their way to
the heart and successfully integrated into it supplementing the muscle already there.
