I am a classical liberal in terms of my views on immediate reform
possibilities.  I favour gradual devolution, privatisation and deregulation
but also would like to ensure that the poorest and most vulnerable are
appropriately compensated for the losses they might suffer in the transition
to a freer society. Greater globalisation and interjurisdictional
