Joviality aside, we could define the One True Green to be the set of all
green things.  In this case, so long as there is a green thing, the Green
still exists.  I presume that this is how you're defining your
consciousness: so long as there is a "John Clark"ness out there, you're
still conscious, where the "John Clark"ness is the set of all matter which
is organized in a Johnclarkian way. 

