damaged beyond any conceivable repair (i.e. burning,
rotting to a pulp, exploding etc.) should be punished 
especially severely (slow & painful death).
--same for destroying a brain in suspension
--(option) executions done publicly in sport stadiums 
(tickets required), footage sold to commercial TV stations 
etc. Money made by these means can help to finance the 
justice system, and a part can go to (family of) the victims.

